{title: Grid Full Syntax}

{start_of_grid shape="1+4x2+4" label="Full Tour"}
A    || G7 . | %  . | %% . | .  . |
     | C7 . | %  . || G7 . | %  . ||
     |: C7 . | %  . :|: G7 . | %  . :| repeat 4 times
Coda | D7 . | Eb7  | D7   | G7 . | %  . |.
